text: Forrest Gump is a 1994 feature film starring Tom Hanks. Forrest Gump may also refer to: * Forrest Gump (novel), 1986 novel by Winston Groom * Forrest Gump (character), main character created by Winston Groom * Forrest Gump - Original Motion Picture Score, film score by Alan Silvestri * Forrest Gump (soundtrack), a soundtrack compilation album of the film * "Gump" (song), a song by Weird Al Yankovic which is about the above character * "Forrest Gump", a song by Frank Ocean from the album Channel Orange
title: Forrest Gump (disambiguation)
